csheets.ext.exportdb.ui

Class UIExportExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • csheets.ui.ext.UIExtension
      • csheets.ext.exportdb.ui.UIExportExtension

  • public class UIExportExtension
extends UIExtension
    This class implements the UI interface extension for the export to hsql db. A UI interface extension must extend the UIExtension abstract class.
    Author:
    1110333 Tiago Pacheco
